name: Agog 4 Planes Intersecting IridOrange
description: @__lindaloh__ 3D sculpture with 2 intersecting planes. One of a collection of 20 individual sculptural pieces from my VR world "Agog", 2021. They are variously luminous, poetic, evocative, shiny, scribbly, wacky, simple, sleek, golden, wonky, compelling, weird, colourful, minimal, maximal, simple, ethereal...
